data.description: Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this adorable home exudes charm from the moment you set eyes on it. Offering a remodeled kitchen and bath, large dining room island with 6 wooden chairs, brand new carpeting, three cozy bedrooms that offer a peaceful retreat, full bath, enclosed front porch and all kitchen appliances that makes this home turnkey. Step outside onto the nice sized deck, where you'll find ample space for outdoor dining, lounging, and soaking up the sun. Fenced in yard, oversized detached garage, mature shade trees and a separate storage shed makes this a true backyard oasis. This adorable well-maintained home offers a perfect blend of indoor comfort and outdoor beauty, providing a tranquil retreat for its lucky occupants to enjoy for years to come. Hurry on in today!!
